&lt;h1 id="take-the-initiative"&gt;Take the initiative&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;The best teacher is the one who suggests rather than dogmatizes, and inspires his listener with the wish to teach himself&lt;/em&gt;. (&lt;a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Edward_Bulwer-Lytton%2C_1st_Baron_Lytton"&gt;Edward Bulwer-Lytton&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;While you should &lt;a href="https://linguista.cn/terencetao/career-advice/orig/talk-to-your-advisor/"&gt;talk to your advisor&lt;/a&gt;, you should not be completely reliant on him or her; after all, you are going to have to do mathematics primarily on your own once you graduate!&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>